Aykon City is a prestigious residential complex comprising two distinct sub-communities: Aykon City East and Aykon City West. This premium project is prominently situated along Dubai's central highway, Sheikh Zayed Road, in the bustling Business Bay district. Designed by ACASA Architects & Engineering Consultants and developed by DAMAC Properties, Aykon City offers a blend of luxurious living and modern amenities.
Aykon City East
Aykon City East consists of four towers, namely Tower A, Tower B, Tower C, and Tower D. These towers are positioned in the eastern section of Aykon City. Construction of this sub-community commenced in the summer of 2016 and was successfully completed by the end of 2021. The towers are interconnected by the Aykon Plaza platform, which provides views of the Aykon Dare tourist attraction. Aykon City East offers a range of facilities, including a large swimming pool, a luxury spa, a beach club, cafes, restaurants, and outdoor spaces for activities like yoga and Tai-Chi.
Aykon City West
Aykon City West features two towers: Tower 1 and Tower 2. Tower 1 is a 34-story Damac Hotel, completed in 2020. Tower 2 is a 30-story residential complex offering luxury apartments with one, two, and three bedrooms. The entire Aykon City complex is safeguarded by a private security company, ensuring round-the-clock security.
Property Offerings
Aykon City offers a diverse range of real estate options, including hotel apartments, private residences, and office spaces. The towers offer captivating views of Sheikh Zayed Road, Safa Park, and Dubai Canal. Currently available for purchase are studios and apartments with 1-3 bedrooms, with property sizes ranging from 40 sqm to 153 sqm. Prices start from AED 796,000 (USD 217,000).
Location and Accessibility
Aykon City enjoys a strategic location adjacent to the picturesque Safa Park. It takes approximately 10 minutes to reach prominent destinations like Dubai Mall, City Walk, and BoxPark. Additionally, it's about 15 minutes away from Palm Jumeirah and Burj Al Arab, and 20 minutes from The Walk JBR. Dubai International Airport is roughly a 30-minute drive away, while the new Al Maktoum International Airport can be reached in about 45 minutes.
Nearby Attractions
Within a 10-minute drive, residents have access to several attractions, including Dubai Bowling Center, Bay Avenue Mall & Park, Dubai Opera House, Souk Al Bahar Market, Dubai Ice Rink, and Mercato Beach (3.7 km away).
Investment Potential
Aykon City stands out as a remarkable project by DAMAC Properties. Its prime location, excellent transport links, and proximity to cultural attractions and business centers make it appealing to families and business professionals alike. The property holds potential for comfortable living as well as long-term investment. Rental properties in Aykon City have the potential to yield up to 5.08% per annum, with the average annual rent for one-bedroom apartments being AED 82,000 (USD 22,300).

building_description:
The Grand at Dubai Creek Harbour by Emaar Properties offers an array of chic amenities including a stylish rooftop lounge offering panoramic views of Burj Khalifa & Dubai Creek Tower. The Grand will be situated near the heart of the dazzling Creek Island, one of Dubai Creek Harbours nine distinct neighbourhoods. Sitting strategically at the intersection of the waterfront between the marina and the promenade, the skyscraper will be in close proximity to both Al Khail Road and Ras Al Khor Road. Reaching Downtown Dubai will not take longer than 10 minutes, while Dubai International Airport will be a mere 15-minute drive away.
Exceeding Expectations and Beyond Imagination:
The Grand will perfectly embody the great ambition of Dubai Creek Harbour. Rising majestically from Creek Island, the 62-story skyscraper will set a new standard for ultramodern living. Envisioned as an Urban Luxe retreat, the cutting-edge waterfront skyscraper is set only steps away from the flourishing marina and vibrant promenade, spoiling the residents with boundless dining, retail and entertainment experiences.
The Grand will overlook the Dubai Creek Harbour marina and the waterfront promenade, giving residents direct access to the world of yachting, as well as a healthy pedestrian-friendly lifestyle. The marina will be a happening destination known for its spectacle and diverse shopping, dining, leisure and nightlife venues. The promenade will be buzzing with cosmopolitan life on beautifully landscaped pedestrian sidewalks brimming with retail outlets.
With The Grand, inspired architecture and superb craftsmanship have unified to create a building that reaches the absolute highest level of contemporary design. The skyscraper offers more than 500 premium apartments, penthouses and podium townhouses with world-class innovative designs to match the visionary surroundings. Choose between 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments, 4-bedroom penthouses, or podium townhouses with stunning views of the Dubai Creek Harbour Marina and the Dubai skyline.
Inspired Design From The Podium Level Up:
The podium level of The Grand comprises of interconnected intimate, communal and active areas creating a welcoming social space. The carefully selected materials have been chosen for their aesthetic qualities as well as efficiency and durability, ensuring The Grand is energy-efficient and environmentally friendly.
Amenities For A 21st Century Superlife:
In addition to having the finest retail and dining outlets at their doorstep, residents of The Grand will have access to a glistening infinity pool with stunning views of the ever-evolving metropolis. They will also have access to cabanas, barbecue areas, childrens play areas and a gymnasium.
Included amongst the broad range of sports and wellness amenities, will be an outdoor tennis court perched up against the 21st-century landscape. The Grand will feature a one-of-a-kind multi-purpose sports area - a space that can transform into several types of sports courts, including volleyball, badminton, and more.
An 'Urban Luxe' Theme Throughout The Community:
Residents of The Grand will have countless family-friendly amenities in the vicinity that will enhance their lives to previously unimaginable levels. From living in the supremely natural surroundings of Dubai Creek, strolling through lush parklands and landscaped promenades, enjoying various leisure and entertainment venues, and taking in the cutting-edge cultural spaces, there will be something to delight everyone.

Exquisite Interiors: Apartments adorned with high-quality materials and furnishings, designed by Tonino Lamborghini's studios.

20% on Booking

Move-In and Settling:

Residents can start moving into their new homes and enjoy the luxurious lifestyle offered by Tonino Lamborghini Residences.



Conclusion
Tonino Lamborghini Residences in Meydan, Dubai, offers an unparalleled living experience with its luxurious apartments and exquisite Italian design. Developed by Gulf Land Property Developers, this prestigious project provides a blend of sophistication and tranquility, making it an ideal choice for discerning homeowners. Six Senses Residences, situated on the illustrious Palm Jumeirah Island in Dubai, represents a groundbreaking addition to the ultra-luxury hospitality chain, Six Senses Hotels Resorts Spas. This project, set for completion in Q4 2024, marks the brand's first foray into the United Arab Emirates, offering a distinctive blend of opulent accommodations and a strong commitment to wellness and sustainability.
Project Development
The development of Six Senses Residences is a collaboration between Six Senses Hotels Resorts Spas, Select Group, and Emirates Strategic Investments Company (ESIC). It encompasses a 60-key luxury hotel and 162 exceptional residences, making it a significant milestone in the realm of high-end hospitality on Palm Jumeirah Island.
Residence Types
Prospective buyers have a diverse range of residence types to choose from, including:

4-bedroom Royal Penthouses with optional private swimming pools.
3 and 4-bedroom Duplex Sky Villas offering panoramic views.
Imperial Penthouses exuding grandeur.
5-bedroom Beach Villas that epitomize luxury coastal living.

Residences span from 2,000 sq. ft to an expansive 14,600 sq. ft, offering a wide array of options to cater to the discerning tastes of buyers.
Sustainable Design and Amenities
The architectural concept of Six Senses Residences is inspired by coral, featuring undulating silhouettes, rooflines, and cellular facades. This design not only provides a unique and distinguished look but also ensures an environment protected from the harsh sun. The development seamlessly combines sustainability and wellness, boasting meticulously landscaped areas, dedicated running tracks, tennis and padel courts, and even a micro farm.
The centerpiece of the property is the luscious Zen garden, complete with mini jebels, courtyards, and valley paths. Residents can engage in a range of activities, including badminton, football, and yoga for their well-being. Natural ponds, Wadi boulders, and palm groves add to the resort-like ambiance. The property also features swimming pools and sundecks surrounded by native vegetation.
Pricing
The starting price for a 2-bedroom penthouse, spanning 2,000 sq. ft, is AED 9.4 million (USD 2.55 million). For those seeking the pinnacle of luxury, opulent 6,000 sq. ft villas are available for a minimum of AED 27 million (USD 7.35 million).
Location and Connectivity
Six Senses Residences enjoys a prime location on Palm Jumeirah's West Crescent, neighboring other renowned luxury hotels. Residents benefit from easy access to prominent F&B venues in Dubai. Additionally, the development is conveniently situated near essential facilities and leisure destinations, including Nakheel Mall, AlIttihad Park, The Palm Tower, and Golden Mile Galleria.
The Palm Jumeirah boasts its own monorail system, providing direct access to the mainland of Dubai via the Sheikh Zayed Road and the Beach Road. Two monorail stations, Atlantis The Palm and Atlantis Aquaventure, are located nearby, and Dubai International Airport is just a 35-minute drive away.
Six Senses Residences sets a new standard for luxury living and hospitality in Dubai, offering an unparalleled blend of opulent residences, wellness, and sustainability in a prime location on Palm Jumeirah Island.

Ellington Beach House, an exquisite residential development by Ellington Properties, is set to redefine luxury living on the iconic Palm Jumeirah in Dubai. This project is slated for completion in Q2 2023 and offers a unique investment opportunity in an area known for its exclusive real estate offerings.
A Rare Gem on Palm Jumeirah
Situated on the prestigious Palm Jumeirah, Ellington Beach House stands as a boutique 7-storey residential development, introducing a new era of luxury to the island. The project features an exclusive selection of 1-3 bedroom apartments and opulent penthouses, boasting meticulously crafted interiors and an array of world-class amenities.
Property Features

Apartment Sizes: Ranging from 1,000 sq. ft to 2,000 sq. ft, the spacious living areas cater to diverse lifestyle preferences.
Amenities: Residents will enjoy access to unparalleled amenities reminiscent of 5-star hotels, including a private beach, swimming pools, a clubhouse, fine dining outlets, parks, open spaces, a hydrotherapy pool, and a bespoke spa center.

Location
Ellington Beach House's prime location along the East Crescent of Palm Jumeirah places it in close proximity to Sofitel Dubai The Palm. This means residents can savor the finest in dining experiences right on their doorstep.
The Luxury of Palm Jumeirah
Palm Jumeirah isn't just a location; it's a lifestyle. The island is renowned for iconic landmarks and hosts some of the most prestigious residential projects in the emirate, such as Serenia Living, Palm Beach Towers, AVA at Palm Jumeirah, Six Senses Residences The Palm, and many more.
Unlock the 10-Year Golden Visa
Investing in Ellington Beach House brings the added advantage of eligibility for a 10-year Golden Visa. By purchasing an off-plan or secondary property with a minimum value of AED 2 million (about USD 545,000), you gain the right to reside, work, and study in the UAE without the need for an Emirati sponsor. The benefits don't stop there. As a Golden Visa holder, you can also bring your family and domestic staff to the UAE, open a bank account, secure private health insurance, obtain a driving license, and more.
Esaad Privilege Card
What's more, as a 10-year Golden Visa holder, you'll be presented with an Esaad privilege card. This card extends an array of discounts and benefits across various sectors, including healthcare, retail, dining, travel, hospitality, and more. This vast network covers over 7,000 brands and businesses in 92 countries, including the UK.
Why Choose Ellington Beach House
Ellington Beach House is not just a residence; it's an investment in a lifestyle of unparalleled luxury. With its prime location on Palm Jumeirah, stunning amenities, and the added advantage of a 10-year Golden Visa and Esaad privilege card, this development is poised to be a coveted gem in the world of high-end real estate. Seize this opportunity to invest in luxury living and secure your path to a golden future in the heart of Dubai.

ORLA Infinity, crafted by OMNIYAT, is a visionary residential project that redefines the concept of luxury living in an unparalleled manner. This project represents a harmonious blend of contemporary elegance and natural splendor, offering a limited collection of 20 exclusive duplex residences.
A Destination for Resort-Style Living
Elegance Amidst Nature
ORLA Infinity is designed to cater to open-minded individuals seeking a resort-style living experience that seamlessly integrates with the surrounding natural beauty. Nestled in the heart of a pristine environment, it offers a unique blend of architectural sophistication and the serenity of sand and sea.
Clarity and Rejuvenation
ORLA Infinity aims to provide its residents with a sense of clarity and rejuvenation. The development has been meticulously planned to create an oasis of tranquility, allowing residents to escape the hustle and bustle of city life and find solace in a natural yet opulent setting.
Exclusive and Personalized Residences
Thoughtfully Positioned Design
Each of the 20 duplex residences within ORLA Infinity has been thoughtfully positioned to maximize the breathtaking views and provide a unique sense of space and privacy. The careful planning ensures that residents can savor the beauty of the surroundings from the comfort of their homes.
Seamless Integration of Spaces
The design of ORLA Infinity is centered around the concept of blending indoor and outdoor spaces effortlessly. This integration allows residents to enjoy the serene surroundings, the state-of-the-art facilities, and the dynamic cityscape beyond, all from the comfort of their residences.
Why Choose Orla Infinity
ORLA Infinity is not just a residential project; it's a masterpiece that offers a lifestyle like no other. OMNIYAT's commitment to elegance, exclusivity, and nature integration comes together in this limited collection of duplex residences. With ORLA Infinity, OMNIYAT has created a haven for those who appreciate the art of refined living in the lap of nature.

The Jewel architecture is of the very highest level, planned by international award winning designers and architects, RMJM and spearheaded by Hazel Wong, known for her exquisite design on Emirates Towers.
The Jewel twin towers rise to an imposing twenty storeys, housing some of the worlds finest apartments Towering over a strategic location on the Dubai Marina and walking distance to the walk at JBR.
The Jewel offers its residents prime marina and sea view. With its exquisite surroundings being based on the worlds largest waterfront development, The Jewels is graced with such elegance and opulence.

Churchill Executive Towers is a complex of two towers in Business Bay in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. Churchill Residency is the taller of the two, standing at 245 m (804 ft). It is a residential tower with 59 floors. The shorter tower is Churchill Executive, an office tower with 42 floors and stands at 172 m (564 ft). The ambiance of the two will be designed to add to the magnificence of the project and provide a highly conducive environment and infrastructure for businesses from around the world that wishing to establish their local, regional and international headquarters here at Business Bay.
The Residency rising in the heart of Dubais new business center, is the address chosen by the few who preferred successfully to mix business with pleasure. Designed to stringent European standards, with breathtaking views of the lake at the center of Business Bay, combined with the peaceful aura of wonderful sculpted and manicured landscapes, The Residency offers an option of one, two and three bedroom apartments, and ultramodern designs planned with contemporary finishes. Comfortable and well-skilled designed penthouses are also available for the exclusively minded individuals. Residents will enjoy amenities such as:- Mini Golf Course,- Relaxation centre with sauna, steam and jacuzzi rooms,- Fully equipped fitness centre and squash courts,- Outdoor swimming pool,- Children's play area and child care centre,- Multi-cuisine cafeteria,- High speed internet connectivity,- 24 hours manned security system,- Motion controlled sensors in all access areas, and- Covered car park.

Marina Wharf blends metropolitan sophistication with the charm of waterfront lifestyle. Coming up right next to the waters, on the inspiring Dubai Marina, this modern classic offers the ultimate lifestyle of penthouses and villas, along with the precious luxury of boundless nature.
Some of the special features of Marina Wharf include:

Stylistic paneling
Unique architecture
Multi-service rooms
Granite backsplash
High quality bathroom fittings
Manicured lawns
Accent lighting
High quality major appliances

Dubai Marina is an urban centre on the water, comparable to the most exclusive waterfront developments in the world's leading cities. Dubai Marina is unlike anywhere else in Dubai, the Middle East and even the world. 
This man-made marina is strategically located near Interchange 5 on Sheikh Zayed Road close to Dubai's well-known landmarks like the Dubai Internet City, The American University of Dubai and the Emirates Golf Club.

building_description:
Beautiful apartments set on a world-class golf course and The Drive at AKOYA.  Golf Promenade   The Drive at AKOYA presents a wonderful mix of variations. These striking buildings are set perfectly between the championship-standard golf course and The Drive at AKOYA, which presents the incredible Beverly Hills lifestyle.
Life at Golf Promenade means having a world-class 18-hole golf course, along with luxury shopping, dining, and entertainment, right there on your doorstep.

The Icon Tower 1 in Jumeirah Lake Towers is a residential tower that consists of 1 bedroom, 2 bedroom as well as studio apartments that vary in size and design.   It has amenities such as recreational parks and lawns, on-site restaurants, retail outlets, childrens creche, gymnasium and health facilities, the tower also possesses of a beautiful lake view on one side and a striking view of Jumeirah Islands on the other.
API Residency at Barsha Heights offers apartments for the perfect residential address to symbolize your deserving lifestyle in Dubai.

Vida Boulevard is a new project by Emaar at Downtown Dubai that combines stylish, world-class design with contemporary finishes and fittings. Residents have access to modern amenities including a swimming pool, fitness centre, and a dedicated area for children, set within the three-storey podium.

Jasmine is a mid-rise residential building by Damac Properties located in Akoya. The project consists of studio, 1, 2, 3 and 4 bedroom apartments. Jasmine is located along Akoya Park (not directly on the golf-course like other condominium developments in Akoya).
MarinaScape is a complex of two residential towers in Dubai Marina. Oceanic Tower consists of 34 storeys and the shorter tower, Avant Tower, consists of 26 storeys.

Emaar introduced Seascape located at Mina Rashid port, which provides an exquisite collection of premium 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments. In Dubai, United Arab Emirates, there is a man-made beach and commercial port called Port Rashid, also called Mina Rashid. One of Dubai's main ports is Mina Rashid, a prominent address with a distinctive tradition. The Mina Rashid Post's renowned Queen Elizabeth II hotel is still a top location for eating, entertainment, and special events with 13 floors.
One of Dubai's main ports and a prestigious address is Mina Rashid, which has won the title of Middle East's Leading Cruise Port eleven times. Emaar embarks on a new venture and debuts their opulent waterfront project in Dubai City's most alluring neighborhood that is ideal for living the regal life.
Location and Proximity:

15-20 Minutes Away - Dubai Marina, JBR, La Mer, Dubai Creek Harbour
20-25 Minutes Away - Palm Jumeirah, CityWalk, Dubai International Airport
25-30 Minutes Away - Dubai Mall, Burj Khalifa, Downtown Dubai

Just like Miami Beach is the getaway destination for the privileged Floridians so will Emaar Beachfront be touted as the preferred resort-style community among Dubais elite. Sunrise Bay perfectly encapsulates the Emaar Beachfront ideology. A premium twin tower of 26 storeys, it is only a few steps away from a glimmering bay and a vibrant marina. The beautifully crafted building blends artfully with its beachfront setting.
A Well Connected Paradise:
The meticulously master-planned Emaar Beachfront is cradled between two of Dubais most desirable destinations, Dubai Marina and areas of new Dubai. Due to the prime location, residents of Sunrise Bay will have easy access to the shimmering beaches, marinas, yacht clubs, malls and dining venues of the Marina and surrounding neighbourhoods. Sunrise Bay also allows for easy access to Sheikh Zayed Road and the city.
A Broad Range Of Apartments & Amenities
The apartments range from 670 sq. ft. for 1-bedroom homes to 2,727 sq. ft. for 4-bedroom residences. The two towers are conveniently connected to each other through a podium deck with world-class sports facilities and private parking spaces. All residents of Sunrise Bay will have access to several retail and healthcare facilities at the ground level.
Proof That Sophistication And Luxury Can Go Hand In Hand
Taking cues from the surrounding material context and reinterpreting this palette into an understated yet elegant form, Sunrise Bay is built for homeowners with a refined, modern taste. Easy-going textures and a refreshing palette of creams, greys, and tons of white are at the heart of Sunrise Bays sophisticated design.
Nothing is out of place in these remastered rooms
The Sunrise Bay master bedrooms are designed to create a sense of calm and beauty so immersive youll never want to leave. Its glamorous and sophisticated in its simplicity, with unexpected textures and colour tones and with attention to details that provide interest and a total respite from city life.
A True Expression Of Yachting Culture
With panoramic balconies that extend the perceptual depth of each apartment and a material composition that references the striking white fibreglass of superyachts  the architecture both physically and perceptually connects the building with the surrounding clear blue waters.
Other projects on Emaar Beachfront are Beach Vista Tower 1, Beach Vista Tower 2, and Marina Vista.

AZIZI FREESIA Residence is an elegant residential building in the heart of Al Furjan, conveniently located next to all the facilities provided in the area. It is part of the Azizi residential community offering a wealth of amenities.
The 11 floor building offers one, two and three-bedroom spacious apartments with fully-fitted kitchens and modern high-quality European finishes. With all the main roads, Sheikh Zayed Road and Emirates Road, conveniently located on the border of this family community, making it one of the most accessible and convenient communities to settle into.

At Sparkle Towers, weve uncovered the secret to happy living, and it consists of a sparkling lifestyle. At Sparkle Towers, you have the opportunity to live, dine, shop and relax within the premises of a hand-crafted, luxury experience. Make every moment of your life count by making your choice a crystal clear choice to a fine-tuned standard of life.
 
Whether it is the panoramic water view or the exclusive lifestyle surroundings of Sparkle Towers, you are guaranteed an experience unlike any other. At Sparkle Towers, we pride ourselves for providing you with the lifestyle that you deserve; a lifestyle beating from the heart of Dubai Marina, one of the concrete wonders of Dubai.
Experiencing Sparkle Towers will excite all your senses, and ensure that not a dull moment passes by.

Savour the beauty of the waterfront lifestyle in a distinctive way in Marina Vista on a gated private island.
Marina Vista is an elegant development from EMAAR -a leading real estate developer- in Dubai Harbour as a part of the gigantic Emaar Beachfront project offering a classy waterfront lifestyle with unprecedented views and specifications.
Marina Vista offers 1, 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments surrounded by breathtaking settings. Every apartment represents the authentic essence of the chic way of living through spacious spaces, high-end finishing, dynamic design, magnificent panoramic views over the Arabian Gulf and Dubai Marina through expansive glass windows.
Bask a wide array of top-notch amenities that celebrate beachfront lifestyle. Whether you are into yachting, swimming in the pool, or working out in the fully-equipped gym, they are there to indulge you. Moreover, world-class dining, shopping, and entertainment venues await you in Emaar Beachfront Boulevard for an unrivalled day-to-day experience.
Living in Marina Vista is the goal of the luxurious waterfront lifestyle journey. Its located within one of the most anticipated mixed-use projects in Dubai in a superior location, with Palm Jumeirah, JBR, and Dubai Marina just a few minutes away.
Other projects on Emaar Beachfront are Beach Vista Tower 1, Beach Vista Tower 2, and Sunrise Bay

Silicon Gates is a prominent residential development in Dubai Silicon Oasis, characterized by its contemporary architecture and comprehensive amenities. This community is ideal for families and professionals seeking a well-connected lifestyle, with easy access to major roadways and key areas in Dubai.
Key Features:

Prime Location: Situated in the tech-focused Dubai Silicon Oasis, offering convenient access to transportation and various commercial hubs.
Variety of Units: The development includes studio, one, two, and three-bedroom apartments, catering to diverse living needs.
Amenities: Residents enjoy a range of facilities, including covered parking, a fitness center, and 24-hour security services, ensuring a safe and comfortable living environment.
Community Living: Silicon Gates promotes a community atmosphere with landscaped gardens and recreational spaces, ideal for family interactions.

Silicon Gates presents an excellent opportunity for those looking to invest in a modern lifestyle within a thriving community in Dubai. With its strategic location and well-designed living spaces, it appeals to a broad range of residents seeking both comfort and accessibility

SP Oasis is a premier residential project located in Dubai Silicon Oasis, designed to offer a modern and comfortable living experience. This development features a variety of apartment types, including spacious studios, 1-bedroom, 2-bedroom, and 3-bedroom units, catering to the needs of families and professionals alike.
Situated in one of Dubais most vibrant and technology-driven communities, SP Oasis boasts state-of-the-art amenities such as a fully equipped gymnasium, swimming pool, children's play area, and 24-hour security. Residents can enjoy the convenience of nearby retail shops, restaurants, and entertainment options, making it an ideal location for those seeking a balanced lifestyle.
With its strategic location, SP Oasis provides easy access to major highways and key areas of Dubai, ensuring a seamless commute to work and leisure destinations. Experience the perfect blend of modern living and community-centric amenities at SP Oasis, your gateway to a contemporary lifestyle in Dubai Silicon Oasis

Discover Mangrove Residences at the heart of Expo City Dubai, offering a wellness-focused, community-centric lifestyle. These spacious apartments and townhouses feature smart, sustainable design with floor-to-ceiling windows, private gardens, and easy access to daily amenities. Enjoy three floors of community spaces, podium gardens, and sky terraces in this modern, 15-minute urban community.

Altia Residence is an upscale residential development located in the innovative Dubai Silicon Oasis (DSO). Known for its contemporary architecture and vibrant community, Altia Residence provides an ideal living environment for families and professionals seeking comfort and convenience in a thriving area.
Key Features:


Strategic Location: Positioned within Dubai Silicon Oasis, residents benefit from excellent connectivity to major highways, making it easy to access key business districts, shopping centers, and recreational facilities throughout Dubai.


Contemporary Living Spaces: The residence offers a variety of thoughtfully designed apartments, featuring spacious layouts, modern finishes, and large windows that maximize natural light and provide pleasant views of the surrounding landscape.


Outstanding Amenities: Altia Residence includes a range of top-tier facilities, such as a swimming pool, fitness center, and landscaped gardens, promoting a healthy and active lifestyle for its residents.


Community-Centric Atmosphere: DSO is recognized for its family-friendly environment, offering parks, playgrounds, and walking paths, fostering a sense of community and connection among residents.


Convenient Services: The development is equipped with essential services, including 24-hour security, concierge assistance, and dedicated parking, ensuring a safe and convenient living experience.


Altia Residence is the perfect choice for those seeking a modern lifestyle in one of Dubai's growing communities. With its stylish living spaces and excellent amenities, this development appeals to individuals and families looking for a harmonious blend of comfort and convenience.

Olivia Residences is a cutting-edge residential building located in the vibrant Dubai Investments Park, United Arab Emirates. This remarkable development symbolizes a harmonious blend of elegance and innovation, redefining contemporary urban living in one of the UAE's most dynamic cities.
Architectural Excellence
Modern Mid-Rise Design
Olivia Residences boasts a modern mid-rise design characterized by clean lines, expansive glass windows, and a fusion of advanced materials. This architectural masterpiece reflects a commitment to delivering the utmost in sophistication and style to its residents.
Striking Faade
The faade of Olivia Residences is a testament to its innovative design. A captivating blend of glazing and wood-textured panels creates a striking contrast against the azure backdrop of the Dubai sky. This unique aesthetic defines and enriches Dubai's urban landscape, making Olivia Residences a standout among its contemporaries.
Location
A Strategic Address
Situated in the heart of Dubai Investments Park, Olivia Residences benefits from a strategic location that offers easy access to key amenities, business hubs, and leisure destinations. Residents will experience the perfect blend of urban convenience and suburban tranquility.
Lifestyle and Amenities
Elegance in Every Detail
Olivia Residences is more than just a place to reside; it's a lifestyle choice. Every aspect of the project is meticulously crafted to provide an elegant living experience. From state-of-the-art facilities to personalized services, residents will enjoy the epitome of modern living.
Urban Oasis
Captivating Views and Natural Harmony
The unique design of Olivia Residences not only defines the urban landscape but also provides residents with captivating views and a connection to natural harmony. It's a tranquil oasis within the bustling city, offering a peaceful retreat from the demands of modern life.
Olivia Residences is a testament to the pursuit of architectural excellence and contemporary living. Its innovative design, prime location, and commitment to elegance make it a symbol of sophistication in Dubai Investments Park. Welcome to a world where elegance and innovation converge at Olivia Residences, setting a new standard for residential living in the dynamic city of Dubai.

One River Point is an extraordinary residential project by Ellington Properties, situated in the heart of Business Bay, Dubai, right on the picturesque waterfront of the Dubai Water Canal. This visionary development promises a luxurious and contemporary lifestyle, offering a range of residential options to suit various preferences and needs.
Residential Diversity
Choose from a selection of thoughtfully designed residential units, including studios, 1-3 bedroom apartments, and spacious 3-4 bedroom penthouses and duplexes. With sizes ranging from 485 sq. ft to 5,850 sq. ft, these residences are designed to provide both comfort and elegance.
Modern Interiors
The interiors of One River Point are adorned with a combination of light colors and dark accents, creating a calming atmosphere and contemporary design. Panoramic windows fill the rooms with natural light, making your home feel both cozy and spacious while offering breathtaking views of the Dubai Water Canal.
World-Class Amenities
Residents of One River Point will experience world-class amenities that enhance their quality of life. From an infinity pool, poolside lounge chairs, and gazebos to a BBQ area, fitness and yoga studios, and a terrace, every aspect of leisure and relaxation has been carefully considered. The complex also features a co-working space with a coffee shop and an exclusive immersion room for those seeking tranquility.
Luxury at Your Doorstep
Upon arrival, a concierge service awaits you in the resident and guest drop-off zone, leading to a bright and spacious lobby furnished with luxurious sofas. This is just the beginning of the premium lifestyle you can expect at One River Point.
Family-Friendly Features
Families will appreciate the separate children's pool and outdoor playground with specially designed soft flooring for safety. An indoor playground with interactive games, bathrooms, and a baby changing station further cater to the needs of families.
Accessible Location
One River Point is conveniently located in Business Bay, offering quick access to a variety of amenities. Enjoy easy access to restaurants, green spaces like Safa Park, and iconic landmarks such as Dubai Mall and Dubai Opera.
Investment Opportunity
Investing in One River Point is not only about securing a luxurious lifestyle but also a solid financial investment. Expect a 15-20% return on investment once the project is completed. One-bedroom apartments in Business Bay typically have an ROI of about 5.8% and can be rented out for attractive annual incomes.
Flexible Payment Plans and Visa Options
Ellington Properties offers advantageous 70/30 payment plans during the off-plan stage, with a required down payment of 20%. Additionally, foreign investors may qualify for UAE residence visas, including a 2-year visa or the prestigious 10-year Golden Visa, covering spouses, children, and domestic staff.
One River Point stands as a testament to luxury living, offering residents a prestigious address in one of Dubai's most sought-after neighborhoods. Whether you seek a serene home or a lucrative investment, this waterfront masterpiece in Business Bay has it all.

The 100 - where luxury meets lifestyle in the heart of Meydan, Dubai. Designed to exceed expectations, The 100 offers a regal living experience with unparalleled views of the iconic Dubai skyline. As one of the most opulent developments in Meydan, The 100 boasts larger living spaces, first-class amenities, and a strategic location that ensures convenience and accessibility to all major destinations in Dubai. Whether you seek royal views, spacious living areas, or world-class amenities, The 100 promises to elevate your lifestyle to new heights. Join us and experience the epitome of luxury living at The 100.
WHY THE 100 MEYDAN?

Royal Size: Offers 35% larger living spaces than standard units.
Royal Views: Residents enjoy breathtaking views of the Dubai skyline.
Royal Location: Provides easy access to Dubais critical destinations via major roads.

LOCATION & NEIGHBORHOOD:
Great Schools: North London Collegiate School, LSG School, ICE School, Dubai International School, Hartland International School.Easy Commute: Convenient public transportation, including future Dubai Metro stations.Shopping Convenience: Shop at Dubai Mall, Dubai Festival City Mall, and Dubai Outlet Mall.Green Spaces: Meydan racecourse, Meydan Cycling and running track, District One Cycling and running track.
15 MINUTES TO:

Downtown Dubai
Business Bay
Dubai International Financial Centre
Dubai International Airport

BUILDING FEATURES:
Provides 153,000 sqft of generous proportioned living spaces.Stretches along 2 separate horizontal sections for quality of living.Residents enjoy a calm oasis in the middle of the city.
AMENITIES:

Tranquil yoga space
Sauna and steam room
Premium lifestyle

PAYMENT PLAN & STARTING PRICES:

Payment Plan: 15% on booking, 45% on handover, 20% at 6 months post-handover, 20% at 12 months post-handover.
Full DLD Waiver
Starting Prices: AED 1.74M for apartments, AED 10.5M for penthouses

Eden House, an epitome of sophistication and exclusivity, is an ultra-luxury development meticulously crafted by H&H in the prestigious Jumeirah area, adjacent to the Dubai Water Canal. Comprising seven floors and a mere 94 high-end units, Eden House stands as a testament to architectural finesse and opulent living.
The development offers a diverse range of residences to cater to varying preferences. From chic studios to lavish 1-3 bedroom apartments and expansive 4-bedroom penthouses, Eden House caters to the most discerning tastes. Additionally, the two duplex penthouses add a touch of grandeur to this exceptional residential offering.
As of Q4 2023, the initial cost per square foot for a property in Eden House ranges from AED 5,000 to 6,000 (USD 1.4K to 1.6K). The payment plan, structured as 60/40, ensures flexibility for potential investors. For detailed financial information, interested parties are encouraged to register on the official website.
Eden House redefines luxury living by providing a unique approach to premium services. Residents are pampered with a curated selection of a la carte services, including but not limited to dry-cleaning, laundry, housekeeping, concierge, and babysitting. These services elevate the living experience to unparalleled levels of comfort and convenience.
Investing in Eden House not only secures an extraordinary living experience but also opens the door to exclusive privileges. Investors have the opportunity to apply for a Golden visa, valid for 10 years. This prestigious visa extends to the investor's spouse, children, and even domestic staff, reinforcing the exclusivity and global appeal of Eden House.
Eden House is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Merging architectural brilliance with unparalleled services and investment opportunities, Eden House stands as a beacon of luxury in the heart of Jumeirah. This development transcends traditional notions of living, offering an experience reserved for those who seek the pinnacle of refinement and sophistication.

MAYA V is an upcoming residential development by London Gate, situated in the highly sought-after Jumeirah Village Triangle district in Dubai. This contemporary project is designed to offer a modern and stylish living experience, featuring a strategic location, well-crafted living spaces, and a host of premium amenities.
MAYA V is strategically located in the heart of Jumeirah Village Triangle, ensuring residents have convenient access to the vibrant cityscape of Dubai. The development provides panoramic views of iconic landmarks, including Dubai Marina and the Burj Al Arab.
The building comprises 6 residential floors and a total of 59 units, featuring a mix of 1-2 bedroom apartments and 2-3 bedroom duplexes. The architectural design emphasizes contemporary aesthetics, with functional layouts to enhance the overall living experience.
London Gate plans to complete the construction of MAYA V by the end of 2024, providing potential homeowners with a clear timeline for occupancy.
The residences in MAYA V boast well-thought-out layouts, including cozy bedrooms with built-in wardrobes, fully equipped closed-type kitchens, and ample storage spaces. Private balconies extend the living space and offer breathtaking views of the city.
MAYA V features a range of premium amenities, including a welcoming lobby with a lounge zone, a fully equipped gym, a swimming pool for both adults and children, and a dedicated playground for the little ones. Residents can unwind in surrounding parks or organize BBQ parties in the designated area.
The building offers private covered parking to residents, ensuring convenient and secure vehicle storage. Additionally, 24-hour security is in place to enhance safety.
Why Choose MAYA V?
MAYA V is not just a residential building; it's a carefully crafted living space that combines modern design, strategic location, and a plethora of amenities to create a vibrant and comfortable community. With its completion slated for the end of 2024, MAYA V promises to be a distinctive addition to the dynamic landscape of Jumeirah Village Triangle, providing residents with a contemporary and enriching lifestyle.

Aura Elegance is an exquisite residential project developed by Aura Infinite Real Estate, situated in the sought-after Dubai Silicon Oasis. This luxurious community embodies a harmonious blend of cutting-edge architecture and contemporary design, providing residents with a comfortable and stylish urban lifestyle.
Key Features:


Elegant Living Spaces: Aura Elegance offers a range of beautifully designed apartments, each featuring high-end finishes and spacious layouts that maximize comfort and functionality.


Prime Location: Located in Dubai Silicon Oasis, residents benefit from convenient access to major transport links, facilitating easy commutes to various parts of the city and nearby attractions.


State-of-the-Art Amenities: The development boasts an impressive array of amenities, including a temperature-controlled swimming pool, a well-equipped gym, a dedicated children's play area, and landscaped gardens designed for leisure and relaxation.


Community Living: Aura Elegance fosters a vibrant community atmosphere, encouraging a lifestyle of togetherness with shared facilities and recreational spaces that cater to families and individuals alike.


Breathtaking Views: Residents can enjoy stunning vistas of the Dubai skyline, enhancing the luxurious living experience with picturesque surroundings.


Aura Elegance stands out as an ideal choice for those seeking a blend of sophistication, modernity, and community spirit in one of Dubai's most innovative areas. Its premium amenities and prime location make it an attractive option for both families and professionals looking for an upscale lifestyle

Mercedes-Benz Places is a collaborative venture between Binghatti Developers and luxury automotive giant Mercedes-Benz, located in the heart of Downtown Dubai. This iconic residential project features 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments as well as penthouses, soaring to an impressive height of 341 meters across 65 floors, redefining opulence in the city's skyline.
Strategically positioned, the development offers unobstructed views of the renowned Burj Khalifa, surrounded by iconic structures such as the Dubai Mall and the Museum of the Future. The partnership between the developer and Mercedes-Benz is dedicated to a customer-centric approach, prioritizing the needs and desires of future residents.
Architectural excellence is a key highlight, boasting floor-to-ceiling heights of 4.2 meters that provide a sense of spaciousness and luxury. Each unit is adorned with a private pool, offering residents an exclusive retreat within their homes. The panoramic views from every unit facing the Burj Khalifa create an awe-inspiring living environment, incorporating the automotive giant's design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity' to create timeless and beautiful spaces.
The project, a result of meticulous planning and design, incorporates smart home technologies and intelligent mobility solutions, aiming to redefine comfort and convenience in modern living spaces. It envisions a lifestyle that seamlessly combines sophistication with the exclusivity of an oasis.
Key highlights include a premium collection of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments and penthouses, an astounding elevation of 341 meters across 65 floors, strategic location in Downtown Dubai, private pools in each residence, and adherence to the Mercedes-Benz design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity.'
In summary, Mercedes-Benz Places is an exclusive residential complex embodying ultra-luxury services, a collaboration between renowned developers and the iconic Mercedes-Benz brand, offering a harmonious oasis of serenity, aesthetic appeal, and a lifestyle that seamlessly blends automotive excellence with architectural grandeur.

A Monumental Collaboration by London Gate and Franck Muller
Embark on a journey into unparalleled luxury with Franck Muller Aeternitas, an architectural marvel set to grace the skyline of Dubai Marina. As the anticipated completion in Q2 2027 approaches, this 106-floor residential masterpiece is poised to redefine opulence and sophistication.
Prime Location: Nestled in the Heart of Dubai Marina, UAEProperty Type: Residential TowerUnits: Offering 1-3BR Apartments and 4-5BR Duplexes
Unmatched Features
Inspired Design: Drawing inspiration from Franck Muller's iconic Aeternitas Mega watchMeticulous Residences: Each unit boasting balconies, premium finishes, and meticulous attention to detailEuropean Elegance: Kitchens and bathrooms adorned with exquisite European marbleBranded Appliances: Equipped with top-tier Bosch and Villeroy & Boch appliances
Unmatched Amenities
Personalized Services: Branded concierge, housekeeping, and business center facilitiesRejuvenation Spaces: Exclusive cigar lounge, The London spa, and tranquil sauna roomsEntertainment Galore: Cinema, music room, and party room for your leisureFamily-Friendly Spaces: Childrens play area, library, and game roomFitness and Recreation: Padel tennis court, yoga studio, swimming pool, and The London gym

Marquis Insignia stands as a remarkable 9-storey residential masterpiece in Arjan, Dubailand, offering a diverse range of apartments designed to harmonize luxury with contemporary living. The development showcases stunning architectural features that utilize a blend of vibrant and neutral tones, creating a serene yet sophisticated environment for its residents.
Key Features:


Diverse Apartment Options: Choose from elegantly designed 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments, each featuring spacious layouts, expansive living areas, and high-quality finishes that redefine luxury living.


Premium Amenities: Residents can enjoy an array of top-tier facilities, including an Olympic-size infinity pool, a botanical garden, outdoor seating areas, a cinema hall, and a jogging track, ensuring a lifestyle of leisure and well-being.


Community and Connectivity: Situated in the rapidly developing district of Arjan, residents benefit from a peaceful atmosphere while remaining close to Dubai's main attractions, shopping centers, and dining options, enhancing both convenience and lifestyle.


Exceptional Design: Each apartment is outfitted with luxurious fittings and features, including spacious bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms, balconies offering panoramic views, and thoughtfully designed kitchens.


Marquis Insignia is not just a home; it's a celebration of modern luxury living, perfectly blending tranquility and accessibility. This development is ideal for those looking to invest in a vibrant community that promises comfort and elegance in every corner.

Cloud Tower A is an impressive residential project located in the sought-after Jumeirah Village Triangle, developed by Tiger Group. Set to be completed in early 2025, this tower boasts contemporary architecture and a variety of unit types, including 1-bedroom, 2-bedroom, and 3-bedroom duplex apartments. The building is designed to provide a serene living experience with a focus on luxury and convenience, catering to both families and individuals looking for an upscale lifestyle in Dubai.
Key Features:


Prime Location: Positioned in Jumeirah Village Triangle, residents benefit from excellent connectivity, with major attractions such as JBR, The Palm Jumeirah, and Dubai Mall just a short drive away.


Diverse Living Options: The tower features 447 residential units, including 1BR, 2BR, and spacious duplex options, accommodating a range of lifestyles and preferences.


Luxurious Amenities: Residents can enjoy a variety of facilities, including an outdoor swimming pool, basketball and tennis courts, a gym, and dedicated children's play areas, all designed to promote an active lifestyle.

building_description:
One Downtown by Binghatti is a visionary residential development located in one of Dubais most coveted addresses  Downtown Dubai. Blending modern elegance with architectural brilliance, this project is designed to redefine luxury living with a bold presence on the citys iconic skyline.
The tower features an exquisite collection of studio to four-bedroom apartments and opulent duplexes, each offering floor-to-ceiling windows, high-end interiors, and panoramic views of landmarks such as the Burj Khalifa and Dubai Water Canal. With a focus on quality, innovation, and functionality, every unit reflects Binghattis signature fusion of art and design.
Residents of One Downtown will enjoy access to a host of lifestyle amenities, including rooftop pools, state-of-the-art fitness centers, wellness zones, children's play areas, and fine retail spaces within the development. Its strategic location ensures unparalleled convenience, with Dubai Mall, financial districts, and cultural venues just minutes away.
Whether as a luxury home or a high-potential investment, One Downtown by Binghatti promises a future-forward living experience in the vibrant heart of Dubai.

Waada  Cascada 1 is the inaugural jewel of the Waada master development by BT Properties, introducing a new chapter of refined, nature-integrated living in Dubai South. Inspired by the vision of seamless harmony between community, comfort, and sustainability, Cascada 1 delivers a lifestyle that is modern yet grounded in human connection and green urbanism.

What Makes It Unique
1. A Legacy Transformed for Dubai
Backed by the pioneering vision of Bahria Town, Cascada 1 represents the groups first bold step into the UAE market. While Bahrias legacy is rooted in Pakistans largest gated communities, Cascada 1 adapts that DNA to Dubais global standardswith smarter infrastructure, sustainable materials, and a people-first design philosophy.
2. A Verdant Urban Oasis
With over 40% of the Waada community dedicated to green corridors, rooftop gardens, and cascading water features, Cascada 1 transforms the idea of vertical living. Unlike conventional towers, this G+16 building is immersed in a larger ecosystem of walkable boulevards, landscaped meditative spaces, and wellness-centric zones.
3. Curated Interiors, Tailored for Life
Each unit, whether a 1, 2, or 3-bedroom apartment, is crafted not just for aestheticsbut for living well. Expect spacious layouts, natural light-maximizing windows, closed kitchens with clean finishes, and thoughtful additions like powder rooms and maids quarters. Every detail is attuned to both family needs and modern tastes.
4. Long-Term Value in a High-Growth District
Cascada 1 sits at the gateway to Expo City and the Al Maktoum Airport corridor, aligning with Dubais long-term growth blueprint (2040 Urban Master Plan). The area is rapidly becoming a magnet for businesses, logistics, and tourismmaking this a prime address for both end-users and investors.

Chelsea Residences 2 is a contemporary residential development located in the heart of Dubai Maritime City, offering a refined blend of coastal charm and urban sophistication. Designed for modern lifestyles, the project features thoughtfully crafted apartments with panoramic views of the Arabian Gulf and the iconic Dubai skyline.
This upscale waterfront community offers residents direct access to Dubais growing maritime districtan area poised to become a hub for marine business, leisure, and living. With sleek architecture, premium finishes, and smart home features, Chelsea Residences 2 delivers a seamless blend of comfort, innovation, and elegance.
Strategically located between Port Rashid and Mina Al Hamriya, the development enjoys excellent connectivity to key areas like Downtown Dubai, DIFC, and Dubai International Airport, while remaining tucked away from the bustle of the city center.
Whether you're looking for an investment opportunity or a lifestyle upgrade, Chelsea Residences 2 presents a rare chance to own a piece of Dubais most promising coastal community.

Binghatti Aquarise  Tower D is a standout residential marvel rising in the heart of Business Bay, Dubai. Crafted by Binghatti Developers, this tower forms part of one of the tallest residential developments in the city, seamlessly blending cutting-edge architecture with refined urban living.
Offering a selection of thoughtfully designed studio to 4-bedroom apartments, Tower D is defined by its flowing design, signature Binghatti aesthetic, and floor-to-ceiling windows that capture sweeping views of the Dubai skyline. Smart home integration and premium interiors reflect the developers commitment to innovation and quality.
Positioned in a prime location with effortless access to Downtown Dubai, Dubai Canal, and major roadways, Binghatti Aquarise  Tower D is not just a homeit's a bold statement of modern luxury. With its rooftop infinity pools, landscaped terraces, fitness facilities, and serene sky gardens, the tower elevates everyday living into an exceptional lifestyle experience.

Whether you're looking for a prestigious address or a high-yield property investment, Akala at Zaabeel 2 delivers on every frontdesign, location, and lifestyle.

Strategically located, Villa del GAVI offers seamless connectivity to key areas of Dubai, making it an ideal choice for those seeking luxury living in a tranquil yet accessible setting. The project is scheduled for completion in the fourth quarter of 2027.

Where Modern Design Meets Resort-Style Living in DLRC

Perfectly Positioned for Work and Play

Why Choose Cove Grand:


Freehold ownership in a rising community


Fully furnished apartments starting at AED 508,000

Delivery by Q1 2027


Cove Grand is not just a place to liveit's a lifestyle choice for those who want more from home.

SAAS Hills by SAAS Properties is set to transform Dubai Science Park with its striking blend of contemporary elegance and natural inspiration. The development features two architecturally stunning towers, their curved silhouettes inspired by the flowing contours of desert rocks, creating a refreshing and organic aesthetic rarely seen in urban Dubai.
This thoughtfully planned community offers a wide array of residencesfrom cozy studios and modern one to three-bedroom apartments to luxurious duplex townhouses and sky villasdesigned to suit every preference and lifestyle. With 857 homes in total, SAAS Hills invites residents to experience a harmonious fusion of space, style, and comfort.
What truly distinguishes SAAS Hills is its focus on health and innovation. Incorporating advanced VLED technology from Vortex Biotech, each residence ensures cleaner air quality by actively combating viruses and allergens, promoting a safer and more comfortable living environment.
Beyond the homes, the project offers extensive amenities spanning over 16,000 sq. ft., including swimming pools, wellness centers, sports courts, a cinema, and retail outlets, all crafted to support a vibrant and balanced lifestyle. Situated minutes away from Dubais key landmarks and business hubs, SAAS Hills combines prime connectivity with the tranquility of Dubai Science Park.
With flexible payment options and a completion target by late 2027, SAAS Hills presents a unique opportunity to invest in a sustainable, tech-forward community designed for the future of urban living.

Blending contemporary architecture with serene views of the surrounding greenery, Rosehill invites residents to experience a new standard of modern urban living.
This mid-rise development is more than just a place to live; its designed to become a vibrant residential sanctuary where convenience, beauty, and functionality come together.
Residences Framed by Nature
Rosehill features a well-balanced mix of 1-, 2-, and 3-bedroom apartments, each crafted with clean lines, generous layouts, and large balconies that open up to views of parks or the championship golf course. Interiors are light-filled and elegant, with finishes that reflect Emaars signature attention to detail and quality.
Whether you're a young couple, a growing family, or an investor, Rosehill offers a lifestyle that feels both relaxed and upscale.
